822
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:48,842
Some of them are just
complicated morasses.

823
00:37:48,842 --> 00:37:50,050
Some of them are just a mess.

824
00:37:50,050 --> 00:37:59,850

825
00:37:59,850 --> 00:38:08,910
