00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:47,600
is going to be my
notation for functions

856
00:39:47,600 --> 00:39:54,050
because I have to write
it a lot-- psi1 and psi2--

857
00:39:54,050 --> 00:40:05,770
and I'll say, of x--
the system-- is down--

858
00:40:05,770 --> 00:40:11,820
